plan.verificationQuery:
SELECT 
  properties->>'name' as name,
  properties->>'league' as league,
  badge_s3_url
FROM cached_entities 
WHERE properties->>'sport' = 'Football'
  AND badge_s3_url IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY properties->>'league', properties->>'name';
